  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);padding:0px;margin:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">以下是台大</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);padding:0px;margin:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">李宏毅老师</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">讲解\"Positional Embedding：如何让 Transformer 知道输入 Token 的顺序\"的视频，来自于他的机器学习2026春季课程：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 24px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);\"><a href=\"https://speech.ee.ntu.edu.tw/~hylee/ml/2026-spring.php\" target=\"_blank\">https://speech.ee.ntu.edu.tw/~hylee/ml/2026-spring.php</a></span></span></p>\n  <p class=\"channels_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <div></div>\n  <p></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;display:inline !important;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">这一讲主要在讲：</span><strong data-start=\"8\" data-end=\"42\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;display:inline !important;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">怎么让 Transformer 知道输入 token 的顺序</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;display:inline !important;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">。先从 self-attention 的基本特性讲起，指出如果没有额外设计，Transformer 对输入顺序本身并不敏感，因此必须显式加入位置信息。接着老师先介绍了&nbsp;</span><strong data-start=\"128\" data-end=\"161\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;display:inline !important;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">Absolute Positional Embedding</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;display:inline !important;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">，也就是把位置向量直接加到 token embedding 上；然后进一步说明，很多语言现象更依赖 token 之间的</span><strong data-start=\"220\" data-end=\"228\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;display:inline !important;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">相对位置</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;display:inline !important;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">，所以又引出了&nbsp;</span><strong data-start=\"236\" data-end=\"269\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;display:inline !important;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">Relative Positional Embedding</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;display:inline !important;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">&nbsp;和&nbsp;</span><strong data-start=\"272\" data-end=\"281\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;display:inline !important;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">ALiBi</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;display:inline !important;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">&nbsp;这类方法。随后重点讲了现在大模型里非常常见的&nbsp;</span><strong data-start=\"307\" data-end=\"315\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;display:inline !important;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">RoPE</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;display:inline !important;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">，它不是简单相加，而是通过对 query 和 key 做旋转，把位置信息自然融入 attention 计算中，因此在 Llama、Qwen、Gemma 等模型中被广泛采用。除此之外，这一讲还讨论了一个更进一步的问题：模型是不是一定需要显式的位置编码，还是有可能在某些结构和训练方式下，部分依靠注意力机制本身学到顺序信息。整体来看，这一讲就是围绕&nbsp;</span><strong data-start=\"489\" data-end=\"535\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;display:inline !important;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">Absolute、Relative、RoPE 以及“没有 Position 行不行”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;display:inline !important;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">&nbsp;这几条主线，系统讲清楚不同位置编码方案分别解决了什么问题、各自有什么特点，以及它们为什么会影响模型对长文本和顺序关系的理解。</span></p>\n  <p><strong data-start=\"252\" data-end=\"305\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webki